台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似<br />\n 一個美國, 一個英國咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:36:31.000Z","msg":"一個香港"}]}